INT. THE IVORY ROOM - BACKSTAGE - CONTINUOUS

Maya is buzzing. Other comics congratulate her. The Stage Manager gives her a thumbs up.

Then, a man in an expensive suit approaches. TALENT AGENT (40s, slick, professional smile).

TALENT AGENT
