Her curiosity says: _Listen._

She follows the voices.

INT. THE IVORY ROOM - BACK HALLWAY - CONTINUOUS

Maya moves quietly. The voices get clearer.

SUIT #1 (O.S.)
You were supposed to be here an hour ago.

UNKNOWN VOICE (O.S.)
(nervous)
I told you, I can't do this anymore. I want out.

SUIT #2 (O.S.)
That's not how this works.

UNKNOWN VOICE (O.S.)
I don't care. I'm done.

