The two suits. A nervous third man. And behind them, a fourth figure in a long trench coat and sunglasses indoors.

Red flags everywhere.

SUIT #2
(to Trench Coat)
Handle it.

The third man's eyes go wide.

THIRD MAN
Waitâ€”no, pleaseâ€”

