# ACT THREE: MIDPOINT CRISIS

EXT. MANHATTAN ALLEY - CONTINUOUS

12 EXT. MANHATTAN ALLEY - CONTINUOUS 12

Maya CHARGES into the nightâ€”straight into TORRENTIAL RAIN. 
She SPRINTS across the street, dress shoes slapping wet 
pavement.

Behind her: SUIT #2. Moving with purpose.

Maya ducks into a narrow alley lined with STACKED BOXES 
