She STOPS. Heart hammering.

Quick scan: Exit at the far end. Stack of boxes to her 
left. Dumpster to her right. Fire escape above.

She presses against the boxes, OUT OF VIEW.

Footsteps approach. Slow. Methodical.

Maya holds her breath, one hand on the boxesâ€”ready to 
