They killed someone. Shot him. Right there in the back hallway.

LARA
And they saw you.

It's not a question.

MAYA
Yes. One of themâ€”the one who gave the orderâ€”he chased me.

Lara's eyes flick back to the monitor showing Suit #2 on his phone.

LARA
(quietly)
That's Marcus Webb. Johnson's head of operations.
(back to Maya)
You're not safe anymore.

MAYA
I need to call the police.

LARA
No.

MAYA
What? Someone justâ€”

LARA
You saw two well-dressed men and a professional at The Ivory Room. That club is owned by people who own the police.
(turns back to monitors)
