Maya stares at her. This stranger who just let her in. Who has surveillance equipment. Who knows things.

MAYA
Who are you?

Before Lara can answer, Bosco nudges Maya's hand again. She looks down at himâ€”at his trusting eyes, his wagging tail.

MAYA (CONT'D)
