MAYA
It's what I do. It's survival.

LARA
Exactly. And what you did tonightâ€”reading your opponent, adapting in real-time, using your environmentâ€”that's the same thing.
(beat)
You've been training your whole life. You just didn't know what for.

Maya looks at the monitors. The files. The evidence of a larger conspiracy.

MAYA
Who are "they"? Really?

LARA
Mr. Johnson. He runs the largest criminal network in New York. Weapons, trafficking, corruption. All hidden behind legitimate businesses.
